## Development

### Setup

    python3 -m venv venv
    source venv/bin/activate
    pip install -r requirements.txt

### Testing

    pytest

### PIPy deployment

Increase the version in `setup.cfg`.
### Github release.

Juste create a new release on github and let the action flow.

####  dev laptop release

    rm dist/*
    python3.11 -m build
    python3.11 -m twine upload dist/*
